The official Python port of rocicorp/fractional-indexing (the Figma /
David-Greenspan fractional-indexing scheme). Vendored verbatim
(byte-faithful, attribution header prepended) per the project's
PORT-not-vendor decision: the `rank` ordering math must live inside
`livespec_runtime`, which has no vendoring machinery and is itself
copied source-only into every consumer's `_vendor/` tree, so the single
ported file rides along automatically. Exposed to livespec call sites
only through the keyword-only wrapper `livespec_runtime.work_items.rank`.

